description:
* This translator app support all major languages like Czech,Danish, Dutch, English, Estonian, Finnish, French, German, Greek, Hebrew, Haitian Creole, Hungarian, Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Lithuanian, Latvian and more..,

* Use this translator you can convert the following types of text:
General;
scientific;
technical;
commercial;
literary;
legal;
educational etc..,


* This Translator app is auto detecting the source language. So no need to set the explicit source language.

* We are translate your text using Bing Translator, so this is very fast and accurate.

* This application not running in the back-ground, so you can save the battery.

* We respect your privacy! we are not saving your information in any where. We are sending the request to the Bing Translator server.

* Easy to use.
